Ross Patterson, Mat Best, and Jarred Taylor are joined by special guests Richard Ryan and Baker Leavitt.  On today's episode we discuss taking the fat one, why grown men don't drink sodas every day, and JT's threesome with another dude. Stay tuned after the show for our new hit song "I'll Take The Fat One".
